 Mr Tom Markram was with his daughter on his farm when the attack took place. Both victims have been rushed to hospital. A description of their attackers has been made known to the community who are currently searching for the three men. One man has been described as short, and was wearing a pair of light blue trousers and a green shirt. The second is slightly taller and was wearing a red jacket and black trousers with a blue backpack. The third attacker has been identified as an older very tall gentleman also wearing a red jacket. Members of the community are urged to be on the look-out for the suspects.  R10 000 reward for information ‘We should kill him’ – Truck driver hears how hijackers argue about his fate #TrafficUpdate: Avoid N4 near Machadodorp VIDEO: Machadodorp two granted bail  • Save our standby number (072 248 3855) and send us a WhatsApp message with the words “Add me” to be added to our broadcast list. • Like us on Facebook, follow us on Twitter and Instagram. • Subscribe to our YouTube channel. • Click on the link to subscribe to our bi-weekly newsletter via email. Contact our news room on our 24 hr standby number 072 248 3855, or send a mail to our editor tobie@mobserver.co.za